=head1 NAME

@XFORM_configinfo@ - Displays useful statistics for all Torrus trees.

=head1 SYNOPSIS

B<@XFORM_configinfo@>

=head1 DESCRIPTION

This command displays information on all available Torrus trees, including 
the names of the trees, counts of leaves, subtrees, views, monitors and
actions, and other information.

=head1 NOTES

See more documentation at Torrus home page: http://torrus.sf.net

